  "instructions": "In this vocabulary set, you will learn the demonstrative words (This, That, Here, There) and some common nouns. Pay close attention to the pattern: 'Ko' words are near you, 'So' words are near the listener.",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "introduction",
      "text": "The pattern is very regular: Ko (near speaker), So (near listener), A (far from both), Do (question). Memorize this structure."
    }
  ],
